## Dependencies

| Package | Version | Purpose |
|---------|---------|---------|
| `dockerode` | Already in `packages/core/package.json` | Docker Engine API client |
| `tar-fs` | Needs to be added | Pack directories into tar streams for `docker.buildImage()` |
| `@types/dockerode` | Already in devDependencies | TypeScript types for dockerode |

Check if `tar-fs` needs to be installed:
```bash
pnpm --filter @gblockparty/core add tar-fs
pnpm --filter @gblockparty/core add -D @types/tar-fs
```

